`★ Insight ─────────────────────────────────────`
Affiliate site architecture matters more than the affiliate links themselves. The review template uses a scoring box with 5 weighted dimensions because readers trust rubrics — they see "8.4/10" and read the breakdown to understand why, which increases time-on-page and dwell time (both Google ranking signals). The coupon site uses localStorage-based search (not server-side) so it works on static hosting like Surge.sh with zero backend cost.
`─────────────────────────────────────────────────`

